0.title: Backend Developer Needed - Python/Django/Flask for High-Performance Web Application
0.description:
We are seeking an expert Backend Developer to design and develop a high-performance web application using modern Python technologies.

**Project Overview:**
You will be responsible for building a scalable, robust backend system that can handle high traffic and complex data processing requirements. This is a comprehensive development project requiring deep expertise in multiple technologies.

**Required Technical Skills:**
• Python (advanced proficiency required)
• Django and Flask frameworks
• PostgreSQL database design and optimization
• Docker containerization
• AWS cloud services and deployment
• CI/CD pipeline implementation and management

**Key Responsibilities:**
• Design and implement high-performance backend architecture
• Develop RESTful APIs and microservices
• Optimize database queries and ensure data integrity
• Set up automated testing and deployment pipelines
• Implement security best practices
• Ensure scalability and performance optimization

**Project Timeline:**
• Estimated duration: 3-6 months
• Project size: Large-scale application development

**What We're Looking For:**
• Expert-level experience in Python backend development
• Proven track record with Django and Flask
• Strong experience with PostgreSQL optimization
• Hands-on experience with Docker and AWS
• Expertise in CI/CD implementation
• Excellent communication skills and ability to work independently
• Strong problem-solving skills and attention to detail

**Budget:** $80-$120/hour based on experience and expertise

We value clear communication, regular updates, and collaborative problem-solving. If you have the skills and experience to deliver a high-quality, scalable backend solution, we'd love to hear from you!
